  "title": "Principal Consultant",
  "description": "<ul><li>Hands-on experience configuring, implementing, and managing DDI (DNS, DHCP, IPAM) solutions</li><li>Expertise with BlueCat Integrity or equivalent enterprise DDI platforms such as Infoblox, VitalQIP, EfficientIP, IPControl</li><li>Strong understanding of DNS architecture,  zones, records, views, polices, DHCP scopes</li><li>Deploy, Configure and maintain DNS infrastructure that provides high available and scalable DNS services across our network</li><li>Good command over IPv4 subnetting and network fundamentals</li><li>Take inventory of the current DNS system and work with IT stakeholders to build a modern DNS System</li><li>Troubleshoot DDI problems and recommend corrective procedures leads troubleshooting DDI issues.</li><li>Configure and maintain DNS,DHCP and IP address management (DDI) Solutions to ensure optimal performance and security</li><li>Monitor and analyze DNS traffic for anomalies and potential threats</li><li>Perform device configurations, internal operating system upgrades and software upgrades and deploy physical/VM appliances to support DNS infrastructure</li></ul>",
